summary: Though Avalugg are commonly used to get cargo through cold areas where it would be hard for humans or vehicles to travel, they...
body: Though Avalugg are commonly used to get cargo through cold areas where it would be hard for humans or vehicles to travel, they can’t carry humans. This is primarily because the body heat a human produces would make them uncomfortable and unwilling to do so, even if you were to use a protective layer.

summary: This is Taters the Rowlet! He’s the first Rowlet in my Pokefamily that I didn’t make myself! He’s technically not a rescue, but...
caption: This is Taters the Rowlet! He’s the first Rowlet in my Pokefamily that I didn’t make myself! He’s technically not a rescue, but I got him at a comic book show in a bargain bin, so I’m pretty sure he’s actually a bootleg, but I love him anyway. He’s almost the last Rowlet in the family, but there are still plenty of Pokemon to cover yet!
